collecting basically all turbulence statistics for incompressible flow

usage:

1. copy all files in to folder 

incompressible_turb_statistic_code/

2. 
have this at the first line of your case.usr code

#include "incompressible_turb_statistic_code/incompressible_turb_statistic_code.usr"

3. 
in userchk:

call incompressible_turb_stat



